00:03:40.330 --> 00:03:43.990
that North Americans have
become more familiar or aware

00:03:43.990 --> 00:03:47.110
of Central America,
is through migrants.

00:03:47.110 --> 00:03:49.270
And more specifically,
through children.

00:03:49.270 --> 00:03:55.560
Central American children who in
